data.description: Discover your very own private retreat on 7.64 acres!  This stunning property begins with a long winding newly graveled driveway pulling up to the spacious carport.  This stunning property also features an inviting pool house, an in-ground pool and a hot tub that conveys! It's the perfect oasis for relaxation, entertainment, and plenty of room to have a mini farm.
